(42, 19, 1, 12, 2, 18, 22, 'Jesus entered and passed through Jericho', 'Healing and Restoration in Jericho', 'Both passages emphasize the significance of Jericho as a location for healing and restoration. In Luke, Jesus passing through Jericho sets the stage for transformative encounters, while in 2 Kings, Elisha heals the waters, restoring life to the land.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
