(42, 19, 2, 14, 17, 5, 6, 'he was rich', 'Riches and Leadership', 'This connection highlights the theme of wealth associated with leadership. Both Zaccheus and Jehoshaphat are described as rich, indicating a link between their status and their roles within their communities.', 'theme', 0.27899999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 19, 3, 42, 23, 8, 8, 'sought to see Jesus', 'Desire to See Jesus', 'This connection highlights the theme of individuals seeking to see Jesus. Both passages emphasize a longing to encounter Him, with one person unable to due to stature and the other filled with joy at the opportunity.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 19, 3, 42, 9, 7, 9, NULL, 'Desire to See Jesus', 'Both passages emphasize a desire to see Jesus. In Luke 19:3, the individual seeks to see Jesus but is hindered, while in Luke 9:7-9, Herod expresses a desire to see him due to the rumors surrounding his identity.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
